      <title>一键设置好小鹤双拼</title>
      <link href="/posts/43502.html"/>
      <url>/posts/43502.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="全拼-双拼"><strong>全拼-&gt;双拼</strong></h2><p>很早就想改用双拼来着，最近看到少数派的文章又加深了我的念头，于是我就去查了查各种双拼方案的异同和优缺点，最后选择了<a href="https://flypy.com">小鹤双拼</a>，如果以前是用全拼，那双拼适应起来也会很快，因为他们本质都是拼音，双拼的原理就是把字拆成声母加韵母<span class="hide-inline"><button type="button" class="hide-button" style="">Click  </button><span class="hide-content">（你问声母和韵母是什么？小学一年级重来吧╰(￣ω￣ｏ)）</span></span>。</p><h2 id="设置双拼"><strong>设置双拼</strong></h2><p>选择了小鹤双拼，却发现 Windows 内置的双拼方案并没有小鹤？！但是让我们一个键一个键去设置又太麻烦（如下图）</p><div  align="center"><img class="inline-img" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Misaka-2020/Debris/Blog_Image/2022-04-23_203937.png" style="height:300px"/><p><strong>让我自己设置，没门</strong>~ ╰(￣ω￣ｏ)</p></div><p>FLYPY <a href="http://flypy.ysepan.com">官网</a> 提供了一种办法，通过修改注册表实现一键设置</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Misaka-2020/Debris/Blog_Image/2022-04-23_205125.png" alt="注册表实现"></p><p>于是我试了试——淦，我的模糊拼音和云联想什么的设置全被还原了，虽然双拼是有了，但是我输入法的设置又得重新来过。所以我觉得这个注册表不理想，那有什么办法能一劳永逸呢( •̀ ω •́ )✧</p><h2 id="自定义注册表"><strong>自定义注册表</strong></h2><p>于是我掏出了万能的 <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com">VSCode</a> 改了改，修改后如下：</p><blockquote><p><strong>直接新建 txt 复制上去然后把后缀改成 reg</strong>，记得先打开<strong>显示扩展名</strong>，改成 reg 以后<strong>双击</strong>就可以了( •̀ ω •́ )y</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[HKEY_CURRENT_USER\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\InputMethod\Settings\CHS]</span><br><span class="line">&quot;EnablePeopleName&quot;=dword:00000000</span><br><span class="line">&quot;EnableUMode&quot;=dword:00000000</span><br><span class="line">&quot;DoublePinyinScheme&quot;=dword:0000000a</span><br><span class="line">&quot;UserDefinedDoublePinyinScheme0&quot;=&quot;FLYPY*2*^*iuvdjhcwfg^xmlnpbksqszxkrltvyovt&quot;</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Expand Double Pinyin&quot;=dword:00000000</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Enable Double Pinyin&quot;=dword:00000001</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Default Mode&quot;=dword:00000001</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Enable Fuzzy Input&quot;=dword:00000001</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Enable Cloud Candidate&quot;=dword:00000001</span><br><span class="line">&quot;Fuzzy Pair Setting&quot;=dword:300</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>与官方提供的相比是不是精简了许多╰(￣ω￣ｏ)</p><p>修改如下：</p><ul><li>删除 Windows 默认值与注册表值相同的条目（写了等于没写）</li><li>开启模糊音（我自己一般用 in-ing &amp; en-eng)</li><li>开启动态词频调整（这样输入法才会记住你的词儿）</li><li>开启输入云建议（有些词太网络化需要云建议）</li><li>关掉人名输入，关掉 U 模式（这俩没什么用）开启 V 模式（Shift+V) <u>V 模式和小鹤兼容，<s>甚至能当计算器使</s></u>😂</li></ul><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Misaka-2020/Debris/Blog_Image/2022-04-23_212317.png" alt="V 模式输入"></p><blockquote><p>模糊拼音条目为 <strong>Fuzzy Pair Setting</strong>，修改为自己需要的(十进制)</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">全不选 —— 0</span><br><span class="line">zh，z —— 1</span><br><span class="line">ch，c —— 2</span><br><span class="line">sh，s —— 4</span><br><span class="line">n ，l —— 8</span><br><span class="line">l，r —— 16</span><br><span class="line">f，h —— 32</span><br><span class="line">wang，huang —— 64</span><br><span class="line">ang，an —— 128</span><br><span class="line">eng，en —— 256</span><br><span class="line">ing，in —— 512</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="练习双拼">练习双拼</h2><p>接下来就是考验你多少天能手熟了</p><p><strong>可以去<a href="https://api.ihint.me/shuang">这里</a>练习练习</strong></p><p>不管你信不信，我两天就速成了╰(￣ω￣ｏ)</p><hr><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Misaka-2020/Debris/Blog_Image/IMG_0561.JPG" alt="Kochou Shinobu"></p>]]></content>
      
      
